  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Creature Type.</strong> You are a Humanoid. You are also considered a goblinoid for any prerequisite or effect that requires you to be a goblinoid.<br /><br /><strong>Size.</strong> You are Small.<br /><br /><strong>Speed.</strong> Your Speed is 30 feet.<br /><br /><strong>Darkvision.</strong> You have Darkvision to a range of 60 feet.<br /><br /><strong>Fury of the Small.</strong> When you damage a creature with an attack or a spell and the creature's size is larger than yours, you can cause the attack or spell to deal extra damage to the creature. The extra damage equals your Proficiency Bonus.</p><p>When you reach character level 5, the extra damage equals twice your Proficiency Bonus.</p><p>You can use this trait a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, regaining all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest, and you can use it no more than once per turn.<br /><br /><strong>Nimble Escape.</strong> You can take the Disengage or Hide action as a Bonus Action on each of your turns.<br /><br /><strong>Stubborn Disposition.</strong> You have Advantage on saving throws you make to avoid or end the &amp;Reference[Charmed apply=false] or &amp;Reference[Stunned apply=false] condition on yourself.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
